lead_paragraph: Iceland have a clean bill of health with captain and long-throw specialist Aron Gunnarsson returning to training on Friday ahead of their European Championship quarter-final against hosts France on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Soccer: Iceland Fully Fit as Captain Gunnarsson Returns to Training
